{"tid":1472312,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"話自己中立 仲更加無性","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:10:12.000Z","uid":36033,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0a23eb9b9c50ec23de37a30a7e2fda331f539a","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n我荃灣返工 8月5罷咗工<br />\n其實一早都預咗有個廢中同事唔會罷咖啦<br />\n我個部門得佢一個唔罷<br />\n當晚荃灣斬人啦<br />\n<br />\n到隔咗幾日見到佢好心問問佢有冇事啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你8月5有冇返工呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到呀 我前一晚去咗元朗 <br />\n     果朝無車出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就好啦 因為荃灣果晚好大件事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有事咩 我唔知喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斬人喎 斬咗好多刀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑衫斬人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑社會呀 撐警果班呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電視無講喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tvb點會講呀 剩係鬧黑衫咖姐佢地<br />\n     仲有警察係民居放催淚彈<br />\n     前面無示威者都照放 小朋友都中彈<br />\n     （我開始眼濕濕）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解警察要咁做 無理由咖喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔知點解 不如你去問警察<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察無可能會傷害無辜市民囉 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有片 可以俾你睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔啦 我不嬲都中立 兩邊都唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n我一直都係微笑同佢講野<br />\n佢一句中立 我即時忍唔住黑面<br />\n第二日 佢仲同其他人講話我好激進<br />\n唔敢同我講野"},{"pid":"9d5ddbd782924177db689799a60fe18cc0cc2e11","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e345d5eeb47cc9f72c4127967ae32bc48ff57f5c","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"最撚憎中立撚<br />\n講撚到禁好聽未姐係助虐撚<br />\n佢哋比藍絲更仆街更垃圾<br />\n希望全香港嘅中立撚<br />\n俾黑警打到仆街<br />\n俾事實佢哋見到"},{"pid":"ad1d98fed9fc8fc348fcb3e71c4f9c918b06ad9b","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e345d5eeb47cc9f72c4127967ae32bc48ff57f5c","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"最撚憎中立撚<br />\n講撚到禁好聽未姐係助虐撚<br />\n佢哋比藍絲更仆街更垃圾<br />\n希望全香港嘅中立撚<br />\n俾黑警打到仆街<br />\n俾事實佢哋見到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"一唔岩聽就話中立<br />\n好on9"},{"pid":"cc05ef21580588c29b0e12751dff4729c70f45aa","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1d98fed9fc8fc348fcb3e71c4f9c918b06ad9b","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e345d5eeb47cc9f72c4127967ae32bc48ff57f5c","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"最撚憎中立撚<br />\n講撚到禁好聽未姐係助虐撚<br />\n佢哋比藍絲更仆街更垃圾<br />\n希望全香港嘅中立撚<br />\n俾黑警打到仆街<br />\n俾事實佢哋見到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"一唔岩聽就話中立<br />\n好on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"我同個中立嘅朋友絕左交<br />\n我估唔到人可以唔識分事非黑白<br />\n仲同我講好多好嘅大陸人<br />\non撚79到"},{"pid":"8b56570d77ee9c60f61555fa40fa813076ae7205","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc05ef21580588c29b0e12751dff4729c70f45aa","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1d98fed9fc8fc348fcb3e71c4f9c918b06ad9b","tid":1472312,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e345d5eeb47cc9f72c4127967ae32bc48ff57f5c","tid":1472312,"uid":227942,"l