l?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmf09kDK.png&h=2492769d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5819b87336e7d99def26bc483564678f25fd699","tid":1472312,"uid":121042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:10:06.000Z","msg":"中立果啲好多都係藍底，係到扮中立，屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade4c372bbd60d89206a4036c1895730739b6bc6","tid":1472312,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"de11996a0cdd869b0278e01cf874e2ae2062dc9b","tid":1472312,"uid":305742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"中立個啲以為自己企係道德高地兩邊唔幫，好有智慧咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事實上根本仲衰過藍絲，佢唔岀聲米姐係默認緊政府所有嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}